  "directive": "RETURN_LEASE_FOR_PIPELINE_REPAIR. Do not authorize a second author retry. The pipeline must reconcile proposal.tex with the already repaired proto-core and invalidate the contradictory reviewer receipt; any later review requires separate authorization.",
